#import "/_lib/0.1.1.typ": *
#show: template

#taxon[Definition]
#title[Flow of a time dependent smooth vectorfield]

A flow of a #link("00AB")[time dependent smooth vectorfield] is a smooth function $Phi: Uu ->  M$ satisfying
1. $Uu subset RR xx M$ is open such that for all $x in M$ the set $Uu nn RR xx {x}$ is an open interval containing $0$.
2. $Phi(0,x) =  x$ _"initial condition"_.
3. $del_(t) Phi(t,x) = X (Phi(t,x),t) $ _"time dependent differential equation"_.
